---
import '../main.css';
import OscillatorContainer from '../containers/OscillatorContainer';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Modal from '../components/Modal.astro';
---

<html lang="en" class="bg-gray-900">
	<Layout title="Tone Generator - WebAudio" description="Generate basic audio waveforms using a digital oscillator.">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center pb-5 text-gradient">Tone Generator</h1>
		<OscillatorContainer client:only="react" />
	</Layout>

	<Modal title="Disclaimer">
		<p>
			This webpage generate audio through oscillators with frequencies ranging from 20 to 20,000 Hz. Prolonged
			listening at high volumes may cause damage to your hearing. It is recommended to
			<strong class="text-gradient">lower the volume</strong> and limit the exposure time.
		</p>
		<p>Incorrect usage could also result in additional risks, including:</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Damage to audio hardware, such as speakers or headphones, due to high-intensity signals.</li>
			<li>Risk of sleep disturbances, anxiety, or stress caused by exposure to intense or annoying sounds.</li>
			<li>Potential interference with medical devices, such as pacemakers, in sensitive patients.</li>
			<li>
				Possibility of causing discomfort or annoyance to individuals hypersensitive to certain frequencies.
			</li>
		</ul>
		<p>
			Please pay attention to the usage of this oscillator and take appropriate precautions to protect your health
			and the integrity of your audio equipment.
		</p>
	</Modal>

	<style>
		li {
			list-style-type: square;
			text-align: left;
			margin-left: 2rem;
		}
	</style>


</html>
